{"type": "article", "id": 42962, "title": "Nike 推出 Flyknit bra，以及，Raf Simons 版的银翼杀手登场 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-07-13T02:28:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 978, "name": "Raf Simons"}, {"id": 12256, "name": "嘻哈"}, {"id": 23079, "name": "Dolce＆Gabbana"}, {"id": 35087, "name": "Golf Wang"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170712234012qwBFSE3a9Yc4reh7.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://fashionista.com/2017/07/glossier-international-shipping-expansion\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美国互联网美妆品牌 Glossier 要进军国际市场</strong></a> | 擅长做美妆 KOL 社区营销的 Glossier 要进军国际市场了，它将于这个月内进入加拿大，今年下半年和明年初将分别扩张英国和法国市场。Glossier 由美妆博主 Emily Weiss 创办于 2014 年，在去年年底完成了 2400 万美元的 B 轮投资。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/chinese-shoppers-help-boost-burberry-revenue-as-europe-spending-slows-10944796/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Burberry 第二季度业绩大涨</strong></a> | 在截止至 6 月 30 日的三个月里，Burberry 的零售额上涨了 13%，至 4.78 亿英镑。得益于中国内地业绩的强劲增长，推动亚太地区实现中个位数百分比的增长；而品牌在英国地区的业绩表现也呈积极增长趋势，推动欧洲、中东、印度、非洲地区实现高个位数增长；美洲地区则出现低个位数百分比的下降。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/louis-vuitton-wins-23-million-counterfeit-lawsuit-in-the-us/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>LV 赢得对中国零售商侵权的诉讼</strong></a> | 在佛罗里达州法庭，LV 赢得了对 200 个在美国销售假冒商品的中国零售商的诉讼，将获得 2300 万美元的赔偿。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2017/07/12/nike-fenom-flyknit-lightweight-sports-bra-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 推出 Flyknit bra</a>。这种运动内衣使用 1 块单层布料，无缝缝合，重量比普通内衣轻了 30%，可以在透气的同时提供运动需要的支撑。Nike 称，这是迄今为止 Flyknit 技术运用在服装行业的最大创新。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101020yCc30s9ZfVXQ2kng.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101011hzDv1mcRqy6AQ8lF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.704738\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101010SkOnea3BVEQ6Y5hF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.724196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101010VPNOe3zduRXQ8oH5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.701354\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/ripndip-supreme-pop-up-store\" rel=\"nofollow\">以中指猫出名的品牌 RIPNDIP 最近来到了洛杉矶 Fairfax</a>，在 Supreme 的旁边开起了快闪店。店内铺设了假草坪和各种有趣的装饰，每位排队等候入场的消费者手中都拿着中指猫版的向日葵气球，还挺好玩的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101600By8DoFrJdAUqTMKk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101554n4HzFpsYlEP31V9L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101554jXcAamr1Jhs5K0Pd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101555E2TtMwZW0Scp5yVa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707131015572Wx0OXZTlS3bEPGq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101555KF27NxPr4O5X1ufb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101556rG9lQMbywuNt3Vhg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101554PrTwEA8CmvqHiLho.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101557VUP5ANbkI0sySe8F.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101557dvBtXrL19iyj5Juq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101558DltyQdN905BnawiM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101558rTZPEcjLbg0M5123.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101559cWFkPJi5rlMDhfda.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>喜欢嘻哈的朋友们，可以去看看 8 月 11 号在日本千叶县市原湖畔美术馆开幕的&nbsp;Rap Museum 。这次展览将以可视化图像和影片的「ART OF RAP」，以及 Rap 文化在实际生活中的体现的「RAP PRACTICE」作为两个中心来展现，届时还会有以 Art 为主题的大约 10 场 Battle。现场 MC 为 DARTHREIDER，评审是市原湖畔美术馆的馆长北川フラム。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707122341261LXI8OZHhD7BYkJ4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.667123\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/fashion-news/lvr-editions-x-dolcegabbana/\" rel=\"nofollow\">意大利品牌 Dolce＆Gabbana 与时尚零售网站 LuisaViaRoma 展开二次合作</a>，带来了四款限量设计。包括涂鸦运动鞋、T 恤、运动腕带及头带，售价 107 至 746 美元不等。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234143VDBQsSPXgWcRMefj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707122341434ah2sZ6bjrQMlp3I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234143JOs3Hf6TncDeZ5xQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234149MDOxHAUT18LnqNB7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>在发布新专辑之前，<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/07/12/golf-wang-restock-ss17/#slide-4\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国说唱歌手 Tyler 主理的 Golf Wang 抢先发布了今夏新品系列</a>。 </p><p>该系列包括长袖、T 恤、帽衫、白色、黑色的帽子和袜子，以薄荷色、橙色、绿色和黄色组成的 GOLF logo 点缀，带来了夏日活力之感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234212fkJu4zlosS0BbNXU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017071223421161jXGIDkJsqy3VoC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707122342124qPkmV7M3iuTKBJO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234210TqpLDO42HPIGa3dz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707122342109a12eZmEK0dnhXNt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234211CpwR1Ziog6HADx8K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234210fdRDGokpY7ZvU6cF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234210okzTxK5Zpgve7aEn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234214PXBgUnVDC8luELyp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>周二晚上，在曼哈顿的天桥下，Raf Simons 的“银翼杀手”们穿着高筒雨靴、大衣、撑着雨伞，走完了<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-spring-collections-2018/new-york/raf-simons/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 2018 春夏系列</a>的秀。 </p><p>这次，Raf Simons 再度与英国艺术家 Peter Saville 合作，带回了 Joy Division 和 New Order 的复古封面图案，结合带有破坏细节的毛衣、箱型西装外套，以及迷幻的霓虹灯，在秀场营造出了满满的电影感。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707122342518JrDHjmGi13voKMN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234251ARuCW6Qaye4L1zYv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707122342511kg2jcPob7Z9KLrf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234251edECuqmkwaYhn9v4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707122342522BirVPTkAIu53Scw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234252oz7nHiCe0A1bJyud.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234253XkgE5N6SzOeQdqYR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234253Uj739YCOTaN1tMxF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234253YpbURJhAa7iyQv0m.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234254cQiblMEr07La8eCk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234254BmXAEMYpO3bjoJr6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234254NS9BdWHw57XJvyun.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017071223425514bTLiED08HRSozy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234255gJt7Sln3rW0VCKuY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234255CvLiJpwBsOZDqu93.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234256tNhkRqQC73cAVafP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234256y2Lkmwx4eKNsgqWi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234256BR3ExIKnW6GfbLSd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234257wDuBo98ANZSHxJev.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234257kvCwiTUKG4aByrgo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234257mlwEv96scfrX2zjK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170712234306THlj7eJLIiwQsUqS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/7/n-hoolywood-2018-spring-summer-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本品牌 N.HOOLYWOOD 也发布了 2018 春夏新品系列</a>。该系列灵感据说是来自美国前总统肯尼迪，有大量象征着校园风格的棒球外套和开襟衫，以及 50 年代感的字体图案。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101056o85xUC0my3RqEbHf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101056swYfneTNrK1lOR9Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101057R1miOuwPLaVNechr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101058XYVMI18Odv6CFxHT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101058Kc04pf1SkeCOqPJi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101059iTUuJy4aBNdtjm7x.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101059IOXp52rBT0Pj1cs9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101059cTvuUX6n0EBDWRfj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101100W2cn4QmK90J6ZPqg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101100jx5oXgUewHiMWCIy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101101TYCBl4HmLPnjf1ZO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707131011014cDF3U5lbWOn7wEo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201707131011021GMXAglIeJkKYnt0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101102l6S2muKt0PVnIRDA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101103ijq7JgGVR8LzM901.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101103IPvZ9oOEFKgfuaLb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101105agjIQyMWxDcGJpzT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101105tXxHdEkcuYmQoh9P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101106HIaqSZ2JCixrg06o.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017071310110680XOEJItbcPm6ZuH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170713101107zFtxAGH5gbK3ewrP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-spring-collections-2018/new-york/raf-simons/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd</a></p>"}